*****status kodlari
Sunucu ve istemciarasindaki temel iliskiyi TCP/IP protokolu saglar.
TCP(Transmission Control Protocol) :
HTTP bunlarin konusma yontemleridir(get,post vs)
HTTP kodlari ise duurm hakkinda bilgi doner


200 => OK
201 => Created
404 => Not found
500 => Internal Server Error
201 => Created
400 => Bad Request
401 => Unauthorized
403 => Forbidden
501 => Not Implemented
